public class DateBox
extends com.totsp.gwittir.client.ui.AbstractBoundWidget<java.lang.String>
implements com.google.gwt.event.logical.shared.ValueChangeHandler

This class is a bit hacked, to support Gwittir validation (if we just had it as an ABW, validation errors would never get to the Gwittir validation s/s). It requires an incoming DateToLongString converter, and an outgoing ShortDate validator

Author:
Nick Reddel
